---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ConceptNotice from '../components/ConceptNotice.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms — DripNow" description="Terms of service for the DripNow pre-launch waitlist site.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/60">Last updated: 10 July 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <ConceptNotice />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-ink/80 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          DripNow is a service operated by Vruzes B.V., registered with the
          Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KvK) under number 64947491, Croeselaan 254,
          3521 CL Utrecht, the Netherlands.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li>Company: Vruzes B.V.</li>
          <li>Chamber of Commerce (KvK): 64947491</li>
          <li>Registered address: Croeselaan 254, 3521 CL Utrecht, the Netherlands</li>
          <li>Contact: <a class="underline hover:text-ink" href="mailto:hello@dripnow.me">hello@dripnow.me</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">2. What DripNow is, today</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          dripnow.me currently offers: (a) an interactive demo that runs on
          fixed sample data, and (b) a waitlist you can join for early access.
          The full product — uploading your own outfit photos to generate a
          personalised, shoppable lookbook — is not yet live. Nothing on this
          site should be understood as an offer of that full service;
          features, availability, and timing may change before launch.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">3. Using the demo</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The demo is provided for illustration only. It uses "canned" sample
          data, not live inventory, live prices, or a real store integration.
          No purchases can be made through the demo, and no real account or
          checkout exists yet.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">4. Joining the waitlist</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          By submitting your email, you ask to be notified about early access.
          We do not guarantee a specific date, order, or that access will be
          granted, and we may change or discontinue the waitlist at any time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">5. Affiliate model</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          When the full product launches, DripNow will earn a commission on
          items purchased through links in your lookbook, at no extra cost to
          you. Commission arrangements with retail partners do not influence
          the price you pay.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">6. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The DripNow name, logo, and the content of this site (text, design,
          images used with permission) belong to us or our licensors. You may
          not copy or reuse them without permission, except as allowed by law.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">7. No warranty, limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This website and its demo are provided "as is" and "as available",
          without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied. To the
          fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Vruzes B.V. is not liable
          for any indirect or consequential loss arising from your use of this
          site. Nothing in these terms limits or excludes liability that cannot
          be limited or excluded under Dutch law, including liability for intent
          or deliberate recklessness.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">8. Changes to the service or these terms</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We may change, suspend, or discontinue any part of this site or the
          future product, and may update these terms as the product develops.
          Material changes will be reflected in the "Last updated" date above.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">9. Governing law and jurisdiction</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          These terms are governed by the laws of the Netherlands. Any disputes
          will be submitted to the competent court of the Rechtbank
          Midden-Nederland, location Utrecht, unless mandatory law provides
          otherwise.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-ink">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Questions about these terms:{' '}
          <a class="underline hover:text-ink" href="mailto:hello@dripnow.me">hello@dripnow.me</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
